data.description: Open House Saturday and Sunday  2:00-4:00!  Light refreshments.  Open concept plan with a soaring 12’  vaulted ceiling . It’s airy, filled with light, and easy one-level living.  The home is well maintained and located on a quiet cul-de-sac.  You have a huge fenced back yard, plenty of room for a garden, chickens, dogs, your hammock, and more.  Even better, subdivide and sell or build on the adjacent acreage.  Buyer to confirm requirements.  Yes, you can entertain, but you can also snuggle by the fireplace in the quiet of the country.  Rich hardwood floors throughout installed in 2021. Fresh paint in several rooms. Bathrooms are tile floors. Washer/dryer convey. The driveway was scraped with new gravel in April. 18 minutes to Ingles. 30 minutes to Downtown Asheville. Come relax on the expansive grassy lawn.  Add a fire pit, and create more happy memories. This is the place for your best life.
